  "detailed_description": "Survival Kingdom is a <strong>turn-based, retro strategy game.</strong><br><br>You are the ruler of a kingdom in a medieval fantasy-pixel world. Embark on an adventure and test your ruling abilities.<br><br>Will your kingdom escape death and achieve glory? Will you be able to survive?<br><br><strong>It all depends on you!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Popularity System: The people are resentful, so treat them well<br></li><li>Upgrade Buildings: You can improve your buildings<br></li><li>Manage your Kingdom: Taxes, Laws and Prison Penalties<br></li><li>28 Endings: Composed of 3 different modules<br></li><li>Honor the gods with statues and sacrifices<br></li><li>Interactive Events<br></li><li>Permadeath</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Survival Kingdom is a <strong>turn-based, retro strategy game.</strong><br><br>You are the ruler of a kingdom in a medieval fantasy-pixel world. Embark on an adventure and test your ruling abilities.<br><br>Will your kingdom escape death and achieve glory? Will you be able to survive?<br><br><strong>It all depends on you!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Popularity System: The people are resentful, so treat them well<br></li><li>Upgrade Buildings: You can improve your buildings<br></li><li>Manage your Kingdom: Taxes, Laws and Prison Penalties<br></li><li>28 Endings: Composed of 3 different modules<br></li><li>Honor the gods with statues and sacrifices<br></li><li>Interactive Events<br></li><li>Permadeath</li></ul>",
